        <h1 class="head">Typography and language: the paragraph</h1>
 		  		                  <p class="post_info clearfix post_info_single"><span>Posted by <a href="http://www.oert.org/en/author/admin/" title="Posts by OERT" rel="author">OERT</a> - Apr 27, 2012 </span>
                     <span class="i_cate"> <a href="http://www.oert.org/en/category/part1/part1-3/" title="View all posts in Page" rel="category tag">Page</a>, <a href="http://www.oert.org/en/category/part1/" title="View all posts in Theory" rel="category tag">Theory</a> </span>
